
== Exercise: Create a feature for your plug-in


=== Create a feature project
		
			Create a
			feature project
			for your
			plug-in and add your plug-in to
			this
			feature. You create a feature project via
			menu:File[New > Other... > Plug-in Development > Feature Project]
			.
		
		
